snippet.title: Part 1: How did I get healthy? With Special Guest, Amber Myers, LCSW
snippet.description:
Part 5A of 5: Naomi's Story Project
________

naomiwrightministries.com

In this part, Amber Myers guides the conversation from her education and professional experience. Naomi has experienced many different struggles in the realm of mental health, but has continued to make tremendous, and surprising, progress. She has come through the other side of many challenges, and fully, whole-heartedly, believes that you can too. Join us for this powerful conversation between two Social Workers, who share a common goal of seeing struggles turned successes. Be the one who prevents the next story here: naomiwrightministries.com/donate

For more information:
- Amber Marie, LCSW
- Book Resource: The Body Keeps the Score: Brain, Mind, and Body in the Healing of Trauma by Bessel van der Kolk
